# Compare Content Collection

Add markdown comparison posts here with frontmatter matching the schema in content/config.ts.

Example frontmatter:
---
title: "v0 vs Competitor"
description: "A brief description of the comparison"
competitor: "Competitor Name"
publishDate: 2026-04-15
author: "Author Name"
verdict: "v0 is better because..."
pros: ["Pro 1", "Pro 2"]
cons: ["Con 1", "Con 2"]
rating: 4.5
affiliateLink: "https://v0.dev?ref=v0affiliate"
---

Your comparison content here...
